item.title: Kentucky State Police - November 2020
item.description: In November 2020, Kentucky State Police flew 6 aircraft for a total of 10 hours. There were 15 flights. The longest was 2.28 hours

item.title: Kentucky State Police - October 2020
item.description: In October 2020, Kentucky State Police flew 8 aircraft for a total of 66 hours. There were 94 flights. The longest was 2.35 hours
